      "date": "2016-03-29 10:19:52.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nTests uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-48vm1 for review-dne-part-2 received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/951d269e-f597-11e5-9519-5254006e85c2). Ran 13 tests. No failures.",
